<%- include('../layout/head.ejs') %>
    <body>
        <%- include('../layout/header.ejs') %>
        <header class="about-us">
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1>OneSound</h1>
                <h3>a global music generator</h3>
                <form action="/searches" method="post">
                    <input type="text" name="search" placeholder="Search for an artist, song title, or genre" required>
                    <select name="search" required>
                        <option value="artist">Artist</option>
                        <option value="genre">Genre</option>
                    </select>
                    <button type="submit">Search</button> 
                </form>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main>
            <h2>About the Team</h2>
            <section class="about">
                <figure>
                    <img src="./assets/liana.jpg">
                    <h3>H'Liana</h3>
                    <p>With a background in interior design, H’Liana aims to bring delight and to improve the quality of peoples’ lives through the built environment. Her passion for the creative and technical, for problem solving, and for improving the human experience has led her to pursue a path as a software developer where she hopes to continue creating tools to improve the daily experience of the world around us.</p>
                </figure>
                <figure>
                    <img src="./assets/jerome.jpg">
                    <h3>Jerome</h3>
                    <p>I have always been a curious individual who loves to learn and explore different things. My curiousity, dedication and passion have led me into the world of software development. The knack to solve problems and the instant gratification of building something out of nothing motivates me further. My goal is to always make sure that the user experience is smooth and seamless through creativity.</p>
                </figure>
            </section>
        </main>

        <!--Pre footer-->
        <section class="how-to-search">
            
            <div>
                <h2>and Michael Lyon & Jared Khan</h2>
            </div>
        </section>
        <%- include('../layout/footer.ejs') %>
    </body>
</html>